{"tid":2171534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府堅拒港貨回歸「中國製造」，美國恩准標籤改動期限延遲45天至11月9日","createTime":"2020-08-24T04:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T07:26:34.000Z","uid":48040,"like":39,"dislike":129,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"edabc4f04b3ba02c8042d61f33c2c1c6d531f6f3","tid":2171534,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:09:27.000Z","msg":"路透香港8月24日- 香港商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華周一表示，美國已將出口當地的&ldquo;香港製造&ldquo;商品改貼&ldquo;中國製造&rdquo;標籤的要求實施日期，由原來的9月25日延展45天至11月9日。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華在生產力促進局的一個網上研討會上作以上表示，他指出，美國方面應一些業界要求，將更改港貨產地來源標記的實施日期延展45天，期間政府會繼續作出相關工作。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，政府已透過駐美國的辦事處向美國方面作出查詢，例如有沒有其他方法是香港可以接受而又符合產地來源要求，以及美方會否有正式的公文向港美業界清楚交代等。<br />\n<br />\n此外，<span class=\"orange\">邱騰華稱政府駐日內瓦辦事處亦已做準備，在世界貿易組織層面方面據理力爭</span>。（完）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.reuters.com/article/hk-china-usa-0824-mon-label-idCNKBS25K0BG?il=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fhk-china-usa-0824-mon-label-idCNKBS25K0BG%3Fil%3D0&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=7b2a7ae4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fhk-china-usa-0824-mon-label-idCNKBS25K0BG%3Fil%3D0&h=f9afd8dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.reuters.com/article/hk-china-usa-0824-mon-label-idCNKBS25K0BG?il=0</a>"},{"pid":"8628e17b136c6c379b1aaa0a3edc5b53bb7a58c1","tid":2171534,"uid":8535,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"帶頭港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85195af588972cd925cbc7a215be9995d14e6938","tid":2171534,"uid":11291,"like":94,"dislike":1,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:10:43.000Z","msg":"政府搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d9754e72c3a093ea346867cf172fda5fec626e","tid":2