4T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"四年前希拉里都係咁覺得"},{"pid":"b7da8a01e329abb118eb3f6745c578ce8936a777","tid":2171534,"uid":2054,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"邱騰華一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「邱騰華，你又搞港獨了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「放售物業，要現金。」便排出三個倫敦物業。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又被人家加關稅！」邱騰華睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你的出口貨物，貼著「中國製造」標籤。」邱騰華便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「香港不能算中國&hellip;&hellip;香港製造！&hellip;&hellip;基本法賦予的事，能加稅麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「影響不大」，什麼「指白為黑」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"1483a28759125b2b2ad009b1629323ab01c1166c","tid":2171534,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"港共：香港不是一個主權國家"},{"pid":"5a105753bc10a033a9f7a4131cc5d88be1848bd2","tid":2171534,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"延咩期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf673f1aee55a337d2aed5206216d37ce12c3724","tid":2171534,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6840f4c752782518be2c63c2e148cb2d683babf","tid":2171534,"uid":286897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"07e7ac029a1eb05602801566fe2b5f809bd671a1","tid":2171534,"uid":48040,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1d0c09d5983f228a3d5aeb9e67744165b73a8182","tid":2171534,"uid":126782,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"11月3號美國大選<br />\n<br />\n「香港製造」延到去 11月 9號 明點解未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"拜登是邱騰華的救命稻草"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:17:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"潛規則係選輸左唔會再做野<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係 下任一上台就大條道理推翻晒你做嘅野"},{"pid":"1b9e78a5532